Mann's Fresh-Cut Sweet Potatoes are rich in vitamins and minerals.

Directions
Keep refrigerated.

Microwave:
Pierce bag with a fork. Place bag on microwave safe dish. Microwave on High for 4-5 minutes (because of differences in microwave ovens heating times may vary). Open bag carefully sweet potatoes will be hot and package will steam.

Stove Top: In a large sauté pan, heat 2 tablespoons of olive oil over Medium-High, heat add package of sweet potatoes. Cover. Stir occasionally for about 15 minutes or until sweet potatoes are tender. Add salt, pepper, garlic salt or your favorite seasoning.

Oven Baked:
Preheat oven to 400 degrees F. Toss 1 package of sweet potatoes with 2 tablespoons olive oil. Arrange sweet potatoes into single layer or large baking sheet. Bake 20 minutes preheated over. Turn potatoes over and bake for 10 minutes more or until crispy brown. Season with salt and pepper or your favorite seasoning.
